<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Elder | Volunteer With Us</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="img/elder.ico" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/global.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/volunteer.css" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <main class="volunteer-simple-container">
      <section class="volunteer-hero">
        <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
        <div class="hero-content">
          <h1>Join Our Compassion Movement</h1>
          <p>Your time can bring light to an elder's life</p>
          <a href="YOUR_GOOGLE_FORM_LINK" class="cta-button" target="_blank"
            >Become a Volunteer</a
          >
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="why-volunteer">
        <h2>Why Volunteer With Elder?</h2>
        <div class="benefits-grid">
          <div class="benefit-card">
            <div class="benefit-icon">👥</div>
            <h3>Build Meaningful Connections</h3>
            <p>
              Network with like-minded individuals who share your passion for
              making a difference. Form bonds that go beyond typical
              friendships.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="benefit-card">
            <div class="benefit-icon">🧠</div>
            <h3>Gain Wisdom from Elders</h3>
            <p>
              Learn life lessons you won't find in textbooks. Our elders are
              living libraries of experience, culture, and history.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="benefit-card">
            <div class="benefit-icon">👵👴</div>
            <h3>Experience Grandparent Love</h3>
            <p>
              If you never had grandparents or miss theirs, this is your chance
              to experience that unconditional love and guidance.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="benefit-card">
            <div class="benefit-icon">🌱</div>
            <h3>Grow as a Person</h3>
            <p>
              Develop patience, empathy, and communication skills that will
              transform you into a better human being.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="transform-section">
        <div class="transform-content">
          <div class="transform-text">
            <h2>How Volunteering Changes You</h2>
            <p>
              Our volunteers consistently report profound personal
              transformations:
            </p>
            <ul>
              <li>💬 Learn to speak with kindness and patience</li>
              <li>🙏 Develop deep respect for all generations</li>
              <li>⏳ Gain perspective on what truly matters in life</li>
              <li>❤️ Experience the joy of selfless giving</li>
              <li>🌍 Become an active, caring citizen</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
              "Volunteering with Elder didn't just change how I see elders - it
              changed how I see myself. The lessons in humility and gratitude
              stay with me every day." - Priya, Volunteer since 2022
            </p>

            <div class="cta-wrapper">
              <a href="YOUR_GOOGLE_FORM_LINK" class="cta-button" target="_blank"
                >Join Us Now</a
              >
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="transform-image">
            <img
              src="img/volunteer-transformation.jpg"
              alt="Volunteer with elder"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="impact-section">
        <h2>The Ripple Effect of Your Time</h2>
        <div class="impact-stats">
          <div class="stat-item">
            <div class="stat-number">150+</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Elders Helped</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-item">
            <div class="stat-number">2,000+</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Volunteer Hours</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-item">
            <div class="stat-number">100%</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Lives Changed</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="impact-text">
          Every hour you give creates a chain reaction of kindness. When you
          brighten an elder's day, they brighten others', and the warmth spreads
          through our entire community.
        </p>

        <div class="cta-wrapper">
          <a href="YOUR_GOOGLE_FORM_LINK" class="cta-button" target="_blank"
            >Start Your Journey</a
          >
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>

    <script>
      function toggleMenu() {
        const nav = document.getElementById("nav-links");
        nav.classList.toggle("show");
      }
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
